<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 04:08:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>热浪：创纪录的62.3摄氏度灼烧里约热内卢</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/heat-wave-record-index-of-62-3c-scorches-rio-de-janeiro/articleshow/108603067.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108603067.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;气象部门表示，周日，令人窒息的热浪创下了新纪录，里约热内卢的高温指数达到了 62.3 摄氏度，为十年来的最高水平。此前的高温指数记录是在11月创下的，当时达到了59.7摄氏度。与此同时，据当局称，极端降雨正在该国南部造成严重破坏，预计下周还将持续。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 03:47:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/heat-wave-record-index-of-62-3c-scorches-rio-de-janeiro/articleshow/108603067.cms</guid></item><item><title>没有对手的球队吗？特朗普排除拉马斯瓦米作为竞选伙伴</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-rules-out-vivek-ramaswamy-as-his-vice-president-candidate/articleshow/108601296.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108601296.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普已决定不选择维韦克·拉马斯瓦米作为副总统候选人，但正在考虑让他担任内阁职务，可能担任国土安全部部长。这一考虑是基于拉马斯瓦米的公开演讲技巧和他作为印度裔美国人的背景，这可能有助于减轻对移民政策的批评。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 02:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-rules-out-vivek-ramaswamy-as-his-vice-president-candidate/articleshow/108601296.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在欺诈案中未能获得 4.54 亿美元保释金，资产扣押迫在眉睫</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-fails-to-get-454m-bond-in-fraud-case-asset-seizures-loom/articleshow/108600550.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108600550.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的 4.54 亿美元保释请求被 30 家担保公司拒绝，这可能导致财产被扣押。他对民事欺诈案件中错误陈述的财产价值提出上诉，截止日期为 3 月 25 日。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 01:02:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-fails-to-get-454m-bond-in-fraud-case-asset-seizures-loom/articleshow/108600550.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙饥荒严重，大规模死亡迫在眉睫：联合国饥饿监测机构</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/famine-level-shortages-in-gaza-mass-deaths-imminent-un-hunger-monitor/articleshow/108599775.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108599775.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:49:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/famine-level-shortages-in-gaza-mass-deaths-imminent-un-hunger-monitor/articleshow/108599775.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京关注乌克兰境内缓冲区，警告俄罗斯与北约冲突距离第三次世界大战仅一步之遥</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-eyes-buffer-zone-inside-ukraine-warns-russia-nato-conflict-just-one-step-from-ww3/articleshow/108599616.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108599616.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:41:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-eyes-buffer-zone-inside-ukraine-warns-russia-nato-conflict-just-one-step-from-ww3/articleshow/108599616.cms</guid></item><item><title>2023年更多中国人结婚，结婚率九年来首次上升</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/more-chinese-tied-the-knot-in-2023-marriage-rates-up-for-1st-time-in-9-yrs/articleshow/108599499.cms</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:35:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/more-chinese-tied-the-knot-in-2023-marriage-rates-up-for-1st-time-in-9-yrs/articleshow/108599499.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队突袭al-Shifa医院，杀死20名哈马斯武装分子</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-troops-raid-al-shifa-hosp-kill-20-hamas-militants/articleshow/108599442.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108599442.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列军队袭击了加沙的希法医院，目标是哈马斯。战斗造成人员伤亡。英特尔揭露哈马斯的存在。 20名武装分子被杀。拜登在战争紧张局势期间与内塔尼亚胡进行了交谈。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:32:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-troops-raid-al-shifa-hosp-kill-20-hamas-militants/articleshow/108599442.cms</guid></item><item><title>又一名印度学生在美国死亡，2024年死亡人数将达到9人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/another-indian-student-dies-in-us-taking-number-of-deaths-to-9-in-2024/articleshow/108599380.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108599380.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:28:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/another-indian-student-dies-in-us-taking-number-of-deaths-to-9-in-2024/articleshow/108599380.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦在阿富汗境内发动空袭</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-carries-out-airstrikes-inside-afghanistan/articleshow/108596841.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108596841.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦周一对阿富汗进行了空袭，以回应最近一次安全哨所袭击事件，造成七名士兵死亡，该袭击事件归咎于边境那边的武装分子。喀布尔批评这些袭击侵犯了阿富汗的主权，并警告说，此类行动可能会造成巴基斯坦无法控制的严重后果。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 18:31:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-carries-out-airstrikes-inside-afghanistan/articleshow/108596841.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国希望海地过渡委员会“尽快”周一准备就绪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-hopes-haiti-transitional-council-ready-as-soon-as-monday/articleshow/108596509.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108596509.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国希望海地成立过渡总统委员会，以解决暴力问题并促进选举，并获得国际社会对稳定局势的支持。该协议是在海地总理阿里尔·亨利决定辞职后达成的。自 2021 年总统被暗杀以来，他一直掌权。该委员会将负责在选举前任命临时政府。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 18:12:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-hopes-haiti-transitional-council-ready-as-soon-as-monday/articleshow/108596509.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列要求世界法院不要针对加沙饥饿问题下令采取新措施</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-asks-world-court-not-to-order-new-measures-over-gaza-hunger/articleshow/108594866.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108594866.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列反对加沙紧急援助令，谴责南非的请求。法律文件驳斥了故意造成的痛苦，批评了滥用程序，否认以平民为目标，并强调对加沙 230 万人的援助受到限制。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 15:54:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-asks-world-court-not-to-order-new-measures-over-gaza-hunger/articleshow/108594866.cms</guid></item><item><title>证监会终身禁止恒大董事长进入证券市场</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-regulator-to-ban-evergrande-chair-from-securities-market-for-life/articleshow/108593875.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108593875.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;房地产巨头恒大集团的子公司周一表示，中国监管机构将终身禁止其董事长进入证券市场，并补充说这家陷入困境的公司将被处以巨额罚款。文件称，恒大“收到中国证监会针对……违法违规行为的行政处罚和市场禁令的预先通知”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 14:28:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-regulator-to-ban-evergrande-chair-from-securities-market-for-life/articleshow/108593875.cms</guid></item><item><title>通胀飙升，Pak cenbank维持利率在22%</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-central-bank-keeps-interest-rate-at-22-amid-alarming-inflation-surge/articleshow/108588699.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108588699.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周五巴基斯坦通胀率达到惊人的32.89%，促使央行连续第六个任期将关键利率维持在22%。央行表示：“应对通胀需要采取谨慎态度，需要维持当前的货币立场，以便到 2025 年 9 月将通胀率降至 5% 至 7% 的目标范围。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 11:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-central-bank-keeps-interest-rate-at-22-amid-alarming-inflation-surge/articleshow/108588699.cms</guid></item><item><title>“冲压压力可以产生恒星”：美国宇航局捕获处女座星系团</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/ram-pressure-can-make-stars-nasa-captures-virgo-galaxy-cluster/articleshow/108594162.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108594162.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; NASA 的哈勃太空望远镜捕捉到了位于处女座、距离我们 5200 万光年的星系 LEDA 42160。冲压压力塑造了它的形状，剥离了恒星形成的物质，但促进了其他区域恒星的形成。 NASA 研究 LEDA 42160 等矮星系，以了解恒星形成的触发因素。明亮的斑块表明活跃的恒星形成区域，揭示了对星系演化的见解。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 15:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/ram-pressure-can-make-stars-nasa-captures-virgo-galaxy-cluster/articleshow/108594162.cms</guid></item><item><title>凯特·米德尔顿 (Kate Middleton) 与威廉王子 (Prince William) 在英国当地的农场商店被发现</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/happy-healthy-kate-middleton-spotted-with-prince-william-at-local-farm-shop-in-uk/articleshow/108586696.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108586696.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 10:47:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/happy-healthy-kate-middleton-spotted-with-prince-william-at-local-farm-shop-in-uk/articleshow/108586696.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国宇航局的 JWST 揭示了对宇宙最小恒星的新见解</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/nasas-jwst-unveils-new-insights-into-the-universes-smallest-stars/articleshow/108585501.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108585501.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国宇航局的 JWST 揭示了对宇宙最小恒星的突破性见解，挑战了现有的恒星形成规范。罗珀博士的发现重新定义了星级分类，影响了教科书。这一发现重塑了恒星演化理论，并强调了 JWST 在空间科学中的变革性作用。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 09:54:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/nasas-jwst-unveils-new-insights-into-the-universes-smallest-stars/articleshow/108585501.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国宇航局的宇宙通信挑战：宇航员有一天会从火星进行视频通话吗？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/nasas-cosmic-communication-challenge-will-astronauts-one-day-video-call-from-mars/articleshow/108585204.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108585204.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; DSOC 技术解决了地球与火星视频通话通信的挑战，解决了延迟、功率限制和大气干扰问题。未来的进步包括星际互联网和用于有效数据传输的更高带宽技术。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 09:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/nasas-cosmic-communication-challenge-will-astronauts-one-day-video-call-from-mars/articleshow/108585204.cms</guid></item><item><title>俾路支团结委员会敦促失踪人员家属反对国家压迫</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/baloch-solidarity-committee-urges-families-of-missing-persons-to-stand-against-states-oppression/articleshow/108583674.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108583674.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俾路支团结委员会和 BYC 敦促支持俾路支省的强迫失踪和国家压迫。不同地区的受害者家属抗议暴行、强迫失踪，并要求为受害者伸张正义。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 08:40:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/baloch-solidarity-committee-urges-families-of-missing-persons-to-stand-against-states-oppression/articleshow/108583674.cms</guid></item><item><title>解读习近平旨在重振中国经济的新口号</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/decoding-xis-new-catchphrase-aimed-at-reviving-chinas-economy/articleshow/108583194.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108583194.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 08:41:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/decoding-xis-new-catchphrase-aimed-at-reviving-chinas-economy/articleshow/108583194.cms</guid></item><item><title>Taters the cat：为什么美国宇航局将猫视频发送到 1900 万英里的深空</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/taters-the-cat-why-nasa-beamed-a-cat-video-19-million-miles-into-deep-space/articleshow/108582993.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108582993.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; NASA 通过向 1900 万英里外发送猫视频来测试深空通信，展示了 DTN 等创新技术的重要性。这项针对猫塔特斯的实验凸显了未来任务中太空通信的进步。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 08:22:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/taters-the-cat-why-nasa-beamed-a-cat-video-19-million-miles-into-deep-space/articleshow/108582993.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>